Watch Loyalty Management Videos

New videos help your users learn about the capabilities of Loyalty Management.

Design Promotions with Global Promotions Management shows how marketing managers can design pricing and loyalty promotions.
Run Promotions with Global Promotions Management demonstrates how system integrators can integrate Global Promotions Management APIs with external systems like shopping site and point-of-sale (POS) systems.
Gamify Member Engagement with Loyalty Management shows how loyalty program managers can design games and run games for loyalty program members.
Reward Members for Shopping at Multibrand (Third-Party) Stores shows how the loyalty program can enable members to receive rewards for purchasing the company's products at multibrand and third-party stores.
